{
  "texts": [
    "We could not \"see\" these themes because of the low number of literature reviews touching on these topics.",
    "In conclusion, using literature reviews as a data source is relevant for understanding the general trends of a research topic in line with the objective of scoping reviews.",
    "However, if the review's objective is to provide detailed trends over time, such as yearby-year analysis, it is better to use all available literature as a source.",
    "We propose three paths for future research:",
    "• Generate more literature reviews about gamification, its use, and its impact in more contexts and specific areas."
  ]
}